<li id="cite_note-behar-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-behar_19-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBeharEne_Metspalu.2C_Toomas_Kivisild.2C_Alessandro_Achilli.2C_Yarin_Hadid.2C_Shay_Tzur.2C_Luisa_Pereira.2C_Antonio_Amorim.2C_Llu.C4.B1.27s_Quintana-Murci.2C_Kari_Majamaa.2C_Corinna_Herrnstadt.2C_Neil_Howell.2C_Oleg_Balanovsky.2C_Ildus_Kutuev.2C_Andrey_Pshenichnov.2C_David_Gurwitz.2C_Batsheva_Bonne-Tamir.2C_Antonio_Torroni.2C_Richard_Villems.2C_and_Karl_Skorecki2006">Behar, Doron M.; Ene Metspalu, Toomas Kivisild, Alessandro Achilli, Yarin Hadid, Shay Tzur, Luisa Pereira, Antonio Amorim, Lluı's Quintana-Murci, Kari Majamaa, Corinna Herrnstadt, Neil Howell, Oleg Balanovsky, Ildus Kutuev, Andrey Pshenichnov, David Gurwitz, Batsheva Bonne-Tamir, Antonio Torroni, Richard Villems, and Karl Skorecki (March 2006). "<a href="http://www.ftdna.com/pdf/43026_Doron.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ftdna.com/pdf/43026_Doron.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Matrilineal Ancestry of Ashkenazi Jewry: Portrait of a Recent Founder Event</a>" (PDF). <i>The American Journal of Human Genetics</i> <b>78</b> (3): 487–97. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1086%2F500307" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1086%2F500307" rel="nofollow">10.1086/500307</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16404693" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16404693">PMID 16404693</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.ftdna.com/pdf/43026_Doron.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.ftdna.com/pdf/43026_Doron.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.ftdna.com/pdf/43026_Doron.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Matrilineal+Ancestry+of+Ashkenazi+Jewry%3A+Portrait+of+a+Recent+Founder+Event&amp;rft